  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::RevManager.NewsEventData
  Headline: Impoverished communities gain a foothold on self-sustainability
  Body: "The mere concept of \u201Cprivate property\u201D has created an artificial
    scarcity of goods bottle-necked by the exchange of capital. By simply sharing
    our resources among the community we sidestep this banditry entirely. A person
    is much more than a consumer."
